! Node.js version not supported
!
! Node.js 18.x reached end-of-life on April 30, 2025 and is no longer supported on Heroku.
!
! Suggestions:
! - Upgrade to a supported LTS version (20.x, 22.x, 24.x)
! - Set `com.heroku.buildpacks.nodejs.support.ignore_eol_error_nodejs = true` in `project.toml` to temporarily bypass this check
!
! https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/nodejs-support#supported-node-js-versions
